title: [Zill/Wright] Advanced Engineering Mathematics 5e + Solutions
description:
Advanced Engineering Mathematics Textbook written by Dennis G. Zill and Warren S. Wright.

This includes the solution manual for the 5th edition. If you're looking for the 4th edition, the 5th and 4th edition are EXTREMELY similar (despite maybe 2 problems per chapter, sometimes none), so I would recommend just downloading the 5th edition with the solutions.

Publisher: Jones & Bartlett Learning; (Dec 21 2009)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0763779660
ISBN-13: 978-0763779665
